Former BBNaija Lockdown housemate, Erica Nlewedim has revealed that her skincare line, ‘Star Girl Skin’ will be launched soon. The actress disclosed this during an interview with Azuka Ogujiuba for her cover of ‘This Day Style’ alongside other Nollywood female film stars. Erica also talked about her foundation, what she desires in her dream man among other things. Taking about the skincare line, she said: “Yes. I’m about to launch my skincare line called ‘Star Girl Skin’. I’m so excited as it’s a real passion of mine. “I believe people should look good in their natural state and that will further enhance beauty when fully glammed up.”